Project Name: Urembo-Wetu

Project Description: Our Page is for a Salon that sells beauty products and offers various salon beauty services. 

Project Objectives:

  Specific Objectives
  Analyze the existing or the current system
  Design the system
  Implement the system
  
  General objectives
  Convert the manual process of salon management into an online platform.
  To provide a user-friendly environment for the management of salon and its customers.
  To provide and generate timely and accurate reports.
  To provide a better searching facility for the management and customers.
  To organize and secure the records in proper implementation and design of the database
